                <h2><a href="@Url.Action("Index", "FooFighters")">Foo Fighters Gigography</a></h2>
                <p>This is a collection of Foo Fighter shows over the past 20 years. Much of this data was colloraborated together with <a href="http://www.foofighterslive.com" target="_blank">www.foofighterslive.com</a>, and is up to date until about 2016.</p>
                <p><a class="btn" href="@Url.Action("Index", "FooFighters")">View details &raquo;</a></p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2><a href="@Url.Action("Index", "iTunes")">iTunes Analysis</a></h2>
                <p>I've been saving my iTunes library files for analysis since 2006. This project is a result of this work. </p>
                <p><a class="btn" href="@Url.Action("Index", "iTunes")">View details &raquo;</a></p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
